Yilong Zhang from Work, Tom Tensfeld and Mike K. Smith from Pfizer, Mike Sackhouse from the Taurus,

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:48.720
Devin Pastore and Evan Eveson from Metrum, and Adrian Waddell and Gabe Becker from Roche.

